This library is licensed under modified BSD License.
===========


*How to build?
===========

$ make

*How to use?
===========

source:

#include "TarArchive.cpp";
int main(void)
{
	TarArchive t;
	t.load("path/to/tar.tar");
	t.getContents("path/to/file").getStream(); //A pointer to "ios"
}

compile:

g++ -std=c++11 source.cpp -I/path/to/header/dir /path/to/libtarpp.a

